product_description:
MASK SET INCLUDES : 1 x Silicone Face Mask Bowl, 1 x Soft Brush, 1 x Stick Spatula, 3 x Measuring Spoons, 1 spray bottle and a small soaking bottle;
HIGH QUALITY : Made with high quality soft PP, light weighted, very stable and flexible. it will last for a long time through many uses;
SOFT & SKIN-FRIENDLY BRUSH : Brushes are very gentle, won't scratch your face, great for applying masks or DIY hair mask;
SPACE SAVING AND HANDY : this facial mask tool set can easily fit in a small makeup bag or handbag, no matter for travel or a short leave, it will be added to your collection to your new must have, never to be worried too big that can’t be carry with you;
MULTIFUNCTIONAL : You can use this facial kit to mix facial masks or hair tinting colors and hair masks. It also can be used for mixing shaving soap cream or foam. Super easy to wash & quick dry.
